sequenceDiagram
    participant Subscriber as User (Subscriber)
    participant Guard as Nginx Guard (Gatekeeper)
    participant Agent as Agent Zero (Brain)
    participant Scout as Scout (Browser)
    participant Web as Internet (External)

    Note over Agent, Scout: Execution Network (Air-Gapped)
    Note over Guard, Agent: Control Network (Internal)

    Subscriber->>Guard: "Research OpenClaw" (Command)
    Guard->>Agent: Forward Command (Authenticated)
    
    activate Agent
    Agent->>Agent: Think: "I need to browse openclaw.ai"
    
    %% Step 1: Browse Command
    Agent->>Scout: Command: browser.goto("https://openclaw.ai")
    activate Scout
    
    %% Step 2: Execution (Isolated)
    Scout->>Web: HTTP GET openclaw.ai
    Web-->>Scout: 200 OK (HTML/JS/CSS)
    Scout->>Scout: Execute JS / Render DOM
    
    %% Step 3: Return Safe Artifacts
    Scout-->>Agent: Return: [Screenshot.png, AccessibilityTree.json]
    deactivate Scout
    
    %% Step 4: Analysis
    Agent->>Agent: Analyze Text Tree (No JS Execution)
    Agent-->>Guard: "Research Complete: Summary..."
    deactivate Agent
    
    Guard-->>Subscriber: Display Result
